'''警察广场1号'''（One Police Plaza）是[[美國|美國]][[纽约市警察局|纽约市警察局]]的总部。大楼位于[[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]][[公园街_(纽约市)|公园街]]，靠近[[纽约市政厅|纽约市政厅]]和[[布鲁克林大桥|布鲁克林大桥]]。其周围是公园街，珍珠街和警察广场。警察广场1号取代了[[中央街240号|中央街240号]]的旧警察总部。

[[File:NYPD_HQ.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Broome_St_NYPD_HQ_2008_jeh.jpg|thumb]]
警察广场1号如同像[[波士顿市政厅|波士顿市政厅]]，平面上設計成矩形，高13层，设计于1973年<ref>{{cite web|title=NYC Police Headquarters|url=http://www.nyc-architecture.com/SCC/SCC020.htm|accessdate=2016-12-15|archive-date=2016-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206164534/http://www.nyc-architecture.com/SCC/SCC020.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

驻楼内新闻机构包括[[美联社|美联社]]、《[[纽约每日新闻|纽约每日新闻]]》、《[[纽约邮报|纽约邮报]]》、《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》等。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Moore|first1=Tina|title=Welcome to The Shack, our new blog from inside NYPD headquarters at One Police Plaza|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/blogs/theshack/shack-new-blog-nypd-headquarters-police-plaza-blog-entry-1.1625405|website=New York Daily News|publisher=New York Daily News|accessdate=29 June 2016|archive-date=2016-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103223348/http://www.nydailynews.com/blogs/theshack/shack-new-blog-nypd-headquarters-police-plaza-blog-entry-1.1625405|dead-url=no}}</ref>

